LEFT JOIN [Accounts] AS [u.SoldToAccount] ON [u].[SoldToAccountNumber] = [u.SoldToAccount].[Number]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.SoldToAccount.BillingAddress] ON [u.SoldToAccount].[BillingAddressId] = [u.SoldToAccount.BillingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.SoldToAccount.MailingAddress] ON [u.SoldToAccount].[MailingAddressId] = [u.SoldToAccount.MailingAddress].[Id]

LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.SoldToAccount.ShippingAddress] ON [u.SoldToAccount].[ShippingAddressId] = [u.SoldToAccount.ShippingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Accounts] AS [u.BilledToAccount] ON [u].[BilledToAccountNumber] = [u.BilledToAccount].[Number]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.BilledToAccount.BillingAddress] ON [u.BilledToAccount].[BillingAddressId] = [u.BilledToAccount.BillingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.BilledToAccount.MailingAddress] ON [u.BilledToAccount].[MailingAddressId] = [u.BilledToAccount.MailingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.BilledToAccount.PhysicalAddress] ON [u.BilledToAccount].[PhysicalAddressId] = [u.BilledToAccount.PhysicalAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.BilledToAccount.ShippingAddress] ON [u.BilledToAccount].[ShippingAddressId] = [u.BilledToAccount.ShippingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Companies] AS [u.BillingEntity] ON [u].[BillingEntityNumber] = [u.BillingEntity].[Number]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.BillingEntity.BillingAddress] ON [u.BillingEntity].[BillingAddressId] = [u.BillingEntity.BillingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.BillingEntity.MailingAddress] ON [u.BillingEntity].[MailingAddressId] = [u.BillingEntity.MailingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.BillingEntity.PhysicalAddress] ON [u.BillingEntity].[PhysicalAddressId] = [u.BillingEntity.PhysicalAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.BillingEntity.ShippingAddress] ON [u.BillingEntity].[ShippingAddressId] = [u.BillingEntity.ShippingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Companies] AS [u.SellingEntity] ON [u].[SellingEntityNumber] = [u.SellingEntity].[Number]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.SellingEntity.BillingAddress] ON [u.SellingEntity].[BillingAddressId] = [u.SellingEntity.BillingAddress].[Id]

LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.ShippingAddress] ON [u].[ShippingAddressId] = [u.ShippingAddress].[Id]
WHERE ([u].[BilledToAccountNumber] = @__accountNumber_0) AND ([u].[InvoiceNumber] = @__InvoiceNumber_1)

LEFT JOIN [Accounts] AS [u.SoldToAccount] ON [u].[SoldToAccountNumber] = [u.SoldToAccount].[Number]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.SoldToAccount.BillingAddress] ON [u.SoldToAccount].[BillingAddressId] = [u.SoldToAccount.BillingAddress].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Addresses] AS [u.SoldToAccount.MailingAddress] ON [u.SoldToAccount].[MailingAddressId] = [u.SoldToAccount.MailingAddress].[Id]
